name: control_index
description: join index to the control table

name: time
description: unique time index: center of bin relative to DATE_BEG

name: packet
description: packet ID from XML TM file

name: parent
description: the parent fits file(s) of this data entry

name: raw_file
description: the RAW TM file from SOC of this data entry

name: scet_coarse
description: coarse part (s) of the spacecraft elapsed time (OBT)

name: scet_fine
description: fine part (bin s) of the spacecraft elapsed time (OBT)

name: obt_end
description: Start of the IDB period in OBT

name: obt_start
description: End of the IDB period in OBT

name: version
description: valid IDB version for the time period

name: triggers
description: trigger counts for the time period

name: counts
description: pixel counts for the time period

name: triggers_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the trigger values

name: variance_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the variance values

name: real_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the real part values

name: imaginary_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the imaginary part values

name: compression_scheme_counts_skm
description: SKM compression schema parameter used for count values

name: compression_scheme_triggers_skm
description: SKM compression schema parameter used for tigger values

name: compression_scheme_variance_skm
description: SKM compression schema parameter used for variance values

name: compression_scheme_spectra_skm
description: SKM compression schema parameter used for spectra values

name: rcr
description: current rate control regime of the instrument

name: energy_bin_mask
description: mask for all 32 energy bands used for the combined data

name: request_id
description: unique request ID for the BSD processing

name: counts_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the pixel count values

name: pixel_mask
description: mask for all 12 detector pixels used for the combined data

name: detector_masks
description: mask for all 32 detectors used for the combined data

name: detector_mask
description: mask for all 32 detectors used for the combined data

name: pixel_masks
description: mask for all 12 detector pixels used for the combined data

name: tc_packet_id_ref
description: reference to the TC type that triggered this TM

name: tc_packet_seq_control
description: refernece to the TC (counter) that triggered this TM

name: num_pixel_sets
description: number of pixelsets in the count structure

name: energy_bin_edge_mask
description: mask of 33 bits - setting start and closing points of enery ranges

name: spectra_err
description: estimated error due to compression alone for the spectra values

name: subspec_num_summed_channel
description: number of summed channel in spectral point
